	<div id="info">
		<p>A <a href="http://processing.org/">Processing</a> application which takes the surface elevation data over a given area of land determined by a given lat/long co-ordinate and displays this as a moveable 3D shape with colour determined by the height at each point. The application take this data from a search using the <a href="https://developers.google.com/maps/">Google Maps API</a>.</p>
